ed="T" n="0868c09"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0868c09"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000005166"><placeName>河中府</placeName><placeName>柏梯山</placeName></placeName><persName key="A013594">文照</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0868c10"/><persName key="A013594">釋文照</persName>，不知何許人也。本敦朴遲訥之人<lb
ed="T" n="0868c11"/>耳，然見佛像則悅懌。一旦詣<placeName key="PL000000005172">柏梯寺</placeName>，<anchor xml:id="beg0868sgsz7"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0868sgsz7"/><persName key="A001779">曇<lb
ed="T" n="0868c12"/>延<roleName>法師</roleName></persName>畫影出家。專念諸經，罔知詮顯，常<lb
ed="T" n="0868c13"/>憤受性昏濁。忽若假寐，見<persName key="A001779">曇延<roleName>法師</roleName></persName>身長<lb
ed="T" n="0868c14"/>一丈，目光四射，謂<persName key="A013594">照</persName>曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A013594">爾</ref>所欲者，<ref type="person" target="#A001779">吾</ref>安能致<lb
ed="T" n="0868c15"/>之？<ref type="person" target="#A001779">吾</ref>有聰明經一卷，求之於彼，必謹而持，<lb
ed="T" n="0868c16"/>取感應若俯拾地芥耳！」即袖中出以授之，<lb
ed="T" n="0868c17"/>則《金剛般若》<ptr target="#n3066"/>也。登即執讀，七過而便驚寤，經<lb
ed="T" n="0868c18"/>猶在目。然後念通無滯，如久習焉。其喉舌<lb
ed="T" n="0868c19"/>間曲折浮沈，尋變入節，非常調也。自此聰<lb
ed="T" n="0868c20"/>敏日新，辯給在口，時謂為<persName key="A002803">觀音</persName>附麗<ptr type="glossary" target="#g157"/>于厥<lb
ed="T" n="0868c21"/>躬也。且曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A001779">我師</ref>是<placeName key="PL000000000075">周</placeName><placeName key="PL000000000105">隋</placeName>國師。凡所纂集義<lb
ed="T" n="0868c22"/>疏，必乘夢寐而神授，<ref type="person" target="#A013594">我</ref>無愧為資矣。」</p>
